# <type>(<scope>): <short description>   ← 72 chars max, lowercase, no period
#
# Types: feat | fix | security | perf | refactor | revert
#        docs | test | chore | build | ci
#
# Append ! for breaking changes: feat!: ...
#
# Examples:
#   feat(oauth): add client_credentials grant
#   fix(http): resolve ssl flag not forwarded to token request
#   chore(deps): bump axios to 2.x
#   ci: add commitlint to pull-request workflow
#
# Body (optional) — wrap at 100 chars, explain WHY not what
#
# Footer (optional):
#   BREAKING CHANGE: describe what breaks and how to migrate
#   Closes #<issue>
#   Co-authored-by: Name <email>
